Package: pmxmock
Title: Structurally Faithful Mock Pharmacometric Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Andrew", "Stein", , "andy.stein@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Generates structurally faithful mock pharmacometric event data
    from an existing dataset without fitting a pharmacokinetic,
    pharmacodynamic, or nonlinear mixed-effects model. Event templates are
    preserved coherently while baseline covariates and endpoint-specific
    longitudinal measurements are blended from compatible source subjects.
